==開發==
此遊戲於2010年10月19日在Level-5 2010年展望新聞發布會上正式公佈<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.andriasang.com/e/blog/2010/10/19/l5vision_2010_live_blog/ |title=Level-5 Vision 2010 Live Blog |author=Anoop Gantayat |date=October 19, 2010 |work= |publisher=Andriasang |accessdate=October 15, 2010 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110717214259/http://www.andriasang.com/e/blog/2010/10/19/l5vision_2010_live_blog/ |archivedate=2011-07-17|deadurl=yes }}</ref>。此遊戲的概念源自Level-5執行總裁[[日野晃博|日野晃博]]，而他隨後就和[[卡普空|卡普空]]交涉關於此計劃的事宜<ref name="1up tgs"/><ref name="Gilbert"/>。[[雷頓教授系列|雷頓教授系列]]的製作者铃木纯指出日野晃博是[[逆轉裁判系列|逆轉裁判系列]]遊戲的支持者，而且他更曾要求铃木製作「與逆轉裁判水平看齊的遊戲」<ref name="1up tgs"/>。開發此遊戲的概念令到逆轉裁判系列製作者巧舟感到十分驚喜。卡普空研究和開發組主管[[稻船敬二|稻船敬二]]指出他八成肯定巧舟會反對這個想法<ref name="eurogamer inafune">{{cite web |url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2010-10-21-inafune-surprised-layton-wright-happened |title=Inafune surprised Layton/Wright happened |first=Rob |last=Fahey |date=October 21, 2010 |work=Eurogamer |accessdate=December 10, 2012 |archive-date=2013-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131020133316/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2010-10-21-inafune-surprised-layton-wright-happened |dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而，日野晃博終究還是成功說服巧舟接受這項建議，並且獲巧舟允許成為此遊戲的主要劇本作者<ref name="eurogamer inafune"/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.andriasang.com/e/blog/2010/10/20/layton_vs_ace_attorney_commentary/ |title=So Who Came Up with This Layton VS Ace Attorney Thing Anyway? |author=Anoop Gantayat |date=October 20, 2010 |work= |publisher=Andriasang |accessdate=October 15, 2010 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120525121353/http://andriasang.com/comqew/layton_vs_ace_attorney_commentary/ |archivedate=2012-05-25 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。而遊戲的動畫則是由動畫製作公司[[BONES_(動畫製作公司)|BONES]]製作<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2012-01-29/professor-layton-vs-ace-attorney-includes-animation-by-bones |title=Professor Layton vs. Ace Attorney Includes Animation by Bones |date=January 29, 2012 |work=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]] |accessdate=December 10, 2012 |archive-date=2013-04-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130428030018/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2012-01-29/professor-layton-vs-ace-attorney-includes-animation-by-bones |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

稻船敬二指出兩間公司合作製作此遊戲時，均願意放棄遊戲角色的獨佔權。他亦指出他們有意「創造一段偉大的歷史，若任何一方不完全投入的話都會導致失敗的歷史」<ref name="eurogamer inafune"/>。日野晃博則認為兩個遊戲的支持者均希望看到雙方角色「一決高下」和「合作面對挑戰」<ref name="eurogamer inafune"/>。卡普空和Level-5均對遊戲作出了貢獻。卡普空主要負責遊戲的視覺設計，而Level-5則負責發佈遊戲<ref name="1up tgs"/>。遊戲角色的設計則混合了兩個遊戲的設計模式，即逆轉裁判系列的詳細設計模式和雷頓教授系列的簡單設計模式<ref name="1up tgs"/>。此遊戲在3DS上支援3D效果，使之成為逆轉裁判系列的首個3D遊戲<ref name="1up tgs"/>。

於2010年[[东京电玩展|东京电玩展]]前的一次日本商業雜誌《鑽石》訪問中，稻船敬二首次提及此遊戲<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.andriasang.com/e/blog/2010/09/22/capcom_level5_team_up/ |title=Capcom and Level-5 Teaming Up |author=Anoop Gantayat |date=September 22, 2010 |work= |publisher=Andriasang |accessdate=October 15, 2010 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120717210621/http://andriasang.com/comphr/capcom_level5_team_up/ |archivedate=2012-07-17 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。2010年9月25日，石井二郎在[[Twitter|Twitter]]與[[史克威爾艾尼克斯|史克威爾艾尼克斯]]的藤澤金對話時意外地提及此遊戲。這樣導致了人們誤以為Level-5正在開發一個逆轉裁判遊戲<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.andriasang.com/e/blog/2010/09/25/level_5_ace_attorney/ |title=Is Level-5 Making a New Ace Attorney? |author=Anoop Gantayat |date=September 25, 2010 |work= |publisher=Andriasang |accessdate=October 15, 2010 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130506024127/http://andriasang.com/compin/level_5_ace_attorney/ |archivedate=2013-05-06 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。石井二郎後來澄清說：「誤解似乎正在蔓延，所以我現在澄清自己其實正在集中開發《[[時光旅行者|時光旅行者]]》」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.andriasang.com/e/blog/2010/09/25/jiro_ishii_no_ace_attorney/ |title=Jiro Ishii Says No to Ace Attorney Repots |author=Anoop Gantayat |date=September 25, 2010 |work= |publisher=Andriasang |accessdate=October 15, 2010 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120721191152/http://andriasang.com/compio/jiro_ishii_no_ace_attorney/ |archivedate=2012-07-21 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。就如其他雷頓教授系列遊戲一樣，雷頓教授和路克的配音工作皆由[[大泉洋|大泉洋]]和[[堀北真希|堀北真希]]負責。而成步堂龍一和綾里真宵的配音工作則是由在[[逆轉裁判_(電影)|逆轉裁判電影]]中飾演主角的[[成宮寬貴|成宮寬貴]]和[[桐谷美玲|桐谷美玲]]負責<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/interest/2011-09-16/professor-layton-vs-ace-attorney-game-cast-revealed |title=Professor Layton vs. Ace Attorney Game's Cast Revealed |date=September 16, 2011 |work=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]] |accessdate=December 10, 2012 |archive-date=2012-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121128224055/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/interest/2011-09-16/professor-layton-vs-ace-attorney-game-cast-revealed |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

此遊戲最先仅於日本發售<ref name="#1">{{cite web |url=http://www.capcom-unity.com/jgonzo/blog/2010/10/19/professor_layton_vs_ace_attorney_announced_for_japan |title=jgonzo > Manage Blog |publisher=Capcom-unity.com |date= |accessdate=2013-04-28 |archive-date=2013-05-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130501003451/http://www.capcom-unity.com/jgonzo/blog/2010/10/19/professor_layton_vs_ace_attorney_announced_for_japan |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2011年7月，Level-5國際美國公司在[[Facebook|Facebook]]上舉辦了一個投票，詢問他們對哪個僅限日本發售的遊戲最有興趣<ref name="level5ia poll">{{cite web|url=http://www.n-europe.com/news-archive/news-level-5-asks-about-localisation-interests|title=Level-5 Asks About Localisation Interests|accessdate=2011-11-04|year=2011|author=Jones, Ashley|work=N-Europe|archive-date=2013-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130715033924/http://www.n-europe.com/news-archive/news-level-5-asks-about-localisation-interests|dead-url=no}}</ref>，結果顯示此遊戲最受歡迎<ref name="poll result">{{cite web |url=http://www.facebook.com/LEVEL5IA/posts/134026613352672 |title=Professor Layton Vs... |publisher=Facebook |date= |accessdate=2013-04-28 |archive-date=2018-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180918010515/https://www.facebook.com/LEVEL5IA/posts/134026613352672 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在此遊戲正式公佈前，卡普空已於2011年東京電玩展上暗示此遊戲的存在<ref name="grlocalization">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamesradar.com/tgs-2011-professor-layton-vs-ace-attorney-confirmed-release-outside-japan/ |title=TGS 2011: Professor Layton vs Ace Attorney confirmed for release outside of Japan? |first=Carolyn |last=Gudmundson |date=September 15, 2011 |work=[[GamesRadar|GamesRadar]] |accessdate=December 10, 2012 |archive-date=2013-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131031204516/http://www.gamesradar.com/tgs-2011-professor-layton-vs-ace-attorney-confirmed-release-outside-japan/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。記者亦因此開始關注此遊戲會否於西方發佈<ref name="Hillier">{{cite web |url=http://www.vg247.com/2012/07/17/retailers-suggests-professor-layton-vs-ace-attorney-headed-west/ |title=Retailers suggest Professor Layton vs Ace Attorney headed west |first=Brenna |last=Hillier |date=July 17, 2012 |work=[[VG247|VG247]] |accessdate=December 10, 2012 |archive-date=2012-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121224083325/http://www.vg247.com/2012/07/17/retailers-suggests-professor-layton-vs-ace-attorney-headed-west/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。日野晃博早前指出此遊戲將於2013年在北美及歐洲發佈<ref name="VG247">{{cite web |url=http://www.vg247.com/2012/12/06/level-5-understanding-japans-best-kept-secret/ |title=Level-5: understanding Japan’s best-kept secret |publisher=VG247 |date=2012-12-06 |accessdate=2013-04-28 |archive-date=2013-04-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130404130827/http://www.vg247.com/2012/12/06/level-5-understanding-japans-best-kept-secret/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但後來Level-5又指出他們並無此計劃<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://kotaku.com/5967355/the-gameplay-in-professor-layton-vs-ace-attorney-is-an-interesting-mix-of-old-and-new |title=The Gameplay in Professor Layton vs. Ace Attorney is an Interesting Mix of Old and New |accessdate=2013-07-15 |archive-date=2013-07-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130709075056/http://kotaku.com/5967355/the-gameplay-in-professor-layton-vs-ace-attorney-is-an-interesting-mix-of-old-and-new |dead-url=no }}</ref>。不过最终在2013年8月，Level-5确认了本作将于2014年初登陆欧洲市场，并在晚些时候将登陆北美市场<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/08/07/professor-layton-vs-ace-attorney-confirmed-for-western-release |title=Professor Layton vs. Ace Attorney Confirmed for Western Releaset |first=Luke |last=Reilly |date=August 7, 2013 |work=[[VG247|VG247]] |accessdate=August 9, 2013 |archive-date=2013-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130811131027/http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/08/07/professor-layton-vs-ace-attorney-confirmed-for-western-release |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 本地化 ===
游戏原本被宣布仅在日本发行，[[卡普空|卡普空]]衡量了社会是否要求游戏本地化在其他地区发售的利益<ref name="#1"/>。2011年7月，Level-5 International America Inc.在[[Facebook|Facebook]]进行民意调查，询问玩家最感兴趣的仅在日本发行的Level-5游戏。《雷顿教授VS逆转裁判》最终获得最多的票数，超6000票<ref name="level5ia poll"/>。尽管官方尚未宣布游行将在日本海外发行，但卡普空在2011年东京电玩展发布的英文新闻稿已经暗示了很多<ref name="grlocalization"/>。记者亦注意到游戏出现在西方国家的各种网上零售商店中，进一步表明日本海外的发布计划<ref name="Hillier"/>。Level-5CEO[[日野晃博|日野晃博]]早前曾表示，《雷顿教授VS逆转裁判》2013年将由其国际工作室在北美和欧洲发布<ref name="VG247"/>。然而，Level-5最近期的声明表示，西方国家的发行尚未证实或公布<ref>http://kotaku.com/5967355/the-gameplay-in-professor-layton-vs-ace-attorney-is-an-interesting-mix-of-old-and-new {{Wayback|url=http://kotaku.com/5967355/the-gameplay-in-professor-layton-vs-ace-attorney-is-an-interesting-mix-of-old-and-new |date=20130709075056 }}></ref>。2013年法国日本博览会期间，被问到游戏的本地化进度时，日野晃博表示“正在制作中”，但当时他并没有讲太多<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nintendoworldreport.com/news/34849 |title=Western Developments for Professor Layton vs. Ace Attorney Teased - News |publisher=Nintendo World Report |date= |accessdate=2013-09-18 |archive-date=2013-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130911003525/http://www.nintendoworldreport.com/news/34849 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。Level-5 International America Facebook主页随后在同一天发布了该信息<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.facebook.com/LEVEL5IA/posts/470266269728703 |title=LEVEL-5 President and CEO, Akihiro Hino... - Level-5 International America Inc. |publisher=Facebook |date=2013-09-08 |accessdate=2013-09-18 |archive-date=2018-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180918010514/https://www.facebook.com/LEVEL5IA/posts/470266269728703 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[任天堂直面会|任天堂直面会]]2013年8月7日最终正式游戏将在美国和欧洲发行，发售日初定于2014年<ref>{{cite web | url = http://kotaku.com/professor-layton-vs-phoenix-wright-is-coming-to-the-u-1053655032 | title = Professor Layton vs. Phoenix Wright Is Coming To The U.S. In 2014 | first = Jason | last = Schrier | date = 2013-08-07 | accessdate = 2013-08-07 | publisher = Kotaku | archive-date = 2013-08-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130811080139/http://kotaku.com/professor-layton-vs-phoenix-wright-is-coming-to-the-u-1053655032 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

